{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were bomb attacks, and we had to go into public bomb shelters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could have found-- been found out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was already curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not supposed to be out in the evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, anyway the life was very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The director of the Jewish Kulturbund who also knew me was very fond of me, and he had a daughter I was very fond of.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so was she, and we are still today-- she survived-- very, very close friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the end of the year's coming up, and I will be in Berlin as their guests.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the Jewish Kulturbund Orchestra-- the Jewish Kulturbund wouldn't last much longer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This [NON-ENGLISH] star got into-- onto our clothing, and the Kulturbund was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then the question was, should we return to Dresden to help our parents?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very soon the deportation started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought that perhaps if all-- we both brothers would be with my parents, and we would be sent to a ghetto or something, situation would be easier for them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, my brother returned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I stayed on in Berlin, and I was put into the German war efforts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to the-- Kulturbund finished, and I went to the organization which assigned you to jobs and said, please, could you give me some kind of work where I preserve my hands?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Said, oh, sure, sure, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're going to go to an factory which makes sanitary articles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lived in the middle of Berlin, in the western part of Berlin, and this victory was all the way in the east.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one hour by subway, or S-Bahn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the one which went outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- well, was in Kopenick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Kopenick was known about two things.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
